Class ZipFile.FileZipEntrySource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.io.ZipFile.FileZipEntrySource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ZipFile.ZipEntrySource, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    ZipFile

    public static class ZipFile.FileZipEntrySource
extends java.lang.Object
    The FileZipEntrySource provides a simple zip entry source which reads its data from a file. That is, this class can be used to read data from a file into a zip entry.
